Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I think I know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A way that we can grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Time to try something new
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Something better
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No more solo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Trust is the way to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:24.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And all we need to do is work together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:25.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ah, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No thanks, no way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I feel the need to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:32.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm smarter, stronger, and I don't need you two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:35.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Stronger? Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll downplay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:42.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How bad you got your rear end handed to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:46.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's time to try a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do we really need a better way to be bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:51.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,United as one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Teamwork? Please, what a fad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:54.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Combine all our strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll go to any length
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:00.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Once we have a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let's go, begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:05.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This time we're gonna win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The ice you're on is thin, so watch what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I know you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:13.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I think I see a grin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For all this pain and torture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:17.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I swear you'll pay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This time we've got a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a long shot this "better way" to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,United as one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll make those ponies so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:30.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If we say "okay"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Would you just go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Once we have a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:37.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We want to break their friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We want to make them weak
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You want revenge on Starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You want that huge physique
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So let's increase our chances
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,By working as a team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To crush our enemies to dust
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And laugh as they all scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:56.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I think I see a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just put me in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Make me queen, you'll be glad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No! Listen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm the best of us three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then you'll see a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:07.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This is my thing, a better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You shall do as I command
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I will rule this triad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A better way to be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now you're making me mad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Won't the ponies be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That would make me so glad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:29.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now we've got a better way to be bad~!